import * as React from "react";

              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              sx={{ color: "#5f656e", px: 4 }}
              size="large"
            >
              Entreprise
            </Button>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
        <Grid container spacing={2} sx={{ pt: 2 }}>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            Price per month
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <Typography variant="body1">US 0$</Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <Typography variant="body1">Starting at US$7.95</Typography>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={3}>
            <Typography variant="body1">Starting at US$7.95</Typography>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
    </>
  );
};
export default Pricing;
